@startuml
actor Staff
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "staff-service" as StaffService
participant "laptop-service" as LaptopService
database "PostgreSQL Laptop DB" as LaptopDB

Staff -> Gateway: POST /api/staff/laptops/
Gateway -> StaffService: POST /staff/laptops/
StaffService -> StaffService: Validate JWT staff
StaffService -> LaptopService: POST /laptops/
LaptopService -> LaptopDB: Insert laptop
LaptopDB --> LaptopService: Laptop row
LaptopService --> StaffService: Created laptop
StaffService --> Gateway: Success response
Gateway --> Staff: Laptop created
@enduml
